Classes in sik.client.user.panels used by sik.client.user
GoodbyePanel
          Panel displayed when a user logs out from a session
HomePanel
          Panel displayed as a the main panel when a user succesfully logs in and creates a session
IntroPanel
          Panel which is shown as the main panel before a user logs in and creates a session.
LogoutPromptPanel
          Panel which is displayed after a pre-defined timeout period to confirm if a user wishes to end their current session or request more time to continue with their session.
ManPinEntryPanel
          Panel displayed to allow a user to log into the system via supplying their unique student ID and pin number rather than using the typical RFID tag to log in.
MapPanel
          Panel which is displayed to show a user an interactive campus map of Manchester metropolitan university.
